{"type": "article", "id": 51916, "title": "金立承认拖欠广告费，杜蕾斯写现代诗 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2018-04-09T04:02:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 49077, "name": "偶像练习生"}, {"id": 7221, "name": "杜蕾斯"}, {"id": 21323, "name": "美图"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 39, "praise_count": 81, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180409115621lS4GaDP6gLhjO9CV.png", "contents": "<h3 nocleanhtml=\"true\">明星又代言了啥</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/04/09/jingboran-becomes-the-first-asian-ambassador-of-clinique/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雅诗兰黛旗下护肤品牌倩碧（Clinique）宣布井柏然出任亚太区首位品牌大使</b></a>。除此之外，雅诗兰黛昨天也发布一支全新 TVC，背景音乐是华晨宇的《异类》，推出恋爱唇膏 310 火星红（华晨宇粉丝昵称为“火星人”）。雅诗兰黛在去年 7 月宣布华晨宇出任其中国区品牌大使。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=j0624sjaxyt&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/04/08/liuwen-becomes-the-face-of-puma-global/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>刘雯升级为 PUMA 品牌全球代言人</b></a>，并拍摄了全新春夏系列广告，展示 PUMA MUSE ECHO EP 系列鞋款及新品服饰。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=a0619xffbyn&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/04/08/nine-percent-supposed-to-be-the-endorser-of-meitu-mobile-phone/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>通过《偶像练习生》出道的 9 名学员以组合形式拿下第一个代言</b></a>。美图继 Angelababy 杨颖后，又签下了 Nine Percent。唔，还是挺符合品牌调性和受众的吧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804091150534kCih9EVZB3otqyQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>值得一提的 Case</h3><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/-jWbmFuG_xzYjhNuZE-3Kg\" rel=\"nofollow\">杜蕾斯写诗</a>，</b>请欣赏?<a href=\"https://m.weibo.cn/status/4226134797263952?wm=3333_2001&amp;sourcetype=weixin&amp;featurecode=newtitle&amp;from=singlemessage&amp;isappinstalled=0\" rel=\"nofollow\">网友评价</a>：都是九年义务教育，为何你那么优秀。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">&nbsp;<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180409112917SDM9rHdIeuBXZ8N2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180409112949Jxc2vOwo8fipWLVq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180409113004WX6DIqgo3eBrGwvN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804091130266x2fRZ0SXhno3LYq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201804091131011vIgDTKaRC5fimbQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180409113120MAHyuY2VqDiWohKB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.333333\" data-format=\"webp\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/04/08/nestle-will-hold-a-social-activity-with-xinqidian-foundation/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>雀巢中国（Nestle）联手北京新起点公益基金会在三里屯举办题为“骨子里的爱不断”的工艺装置艺术展</b></a>，希望能通过这场活动来吸引更多人关注残疾人的生存问题。此前雀巢发布了三段视频       《吹响生命乐章的小号手》、《不言放弃的制片人》和《轮椅上的摩托车赛手》。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=b0623wzj9uh&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p class=\"\"><b><a href=\"http://www.madisonboom.com/2018/04/08/whats-nicki-manaj-doing-in-mercedess-new-ad/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nicki Minaj 客串了奔驰 A-Class 新广告</a></b>。据说是流媒体服务平台 Tidal 与奔驰合作的前奏。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=x1336vbzr6c&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>其他，也挺重要</h3><p><a href=\"http://tech.163.com/18/0408/13/DESF5IKO00097U7S.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>金立副总裁回应 60 亿广告费：确实拖欠，不要落井下石</b></a>。4 月 8 日消息，金立董事长刘立荣资产被冻结之后，金立欠款百亿的问题就被曝出。近期，有媒体爆料称金立曾花 60 亿请冯小刚等明星代言，负债百亿。对此，金立副总裁俞雷在微博上进行了回应称，金立确实欠了钱，但都会还，希望大家给金立点时间，不要落井下石。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来源：杜蕾斯</p>"}